<a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?tstr=%e8%af%97%e7%bb%8f">诗经</a>
<span>，</span><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?tstr=%e5%93%80%e6%80%a8">哀怨</a>
</div>
