<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_8b849809138d.aspx"><b>周颂·武</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson8b849809138d">
<p>於皇武王！无竞维烈。允文文王，克开厥后。嗣武受之，胜殷遏刘，耆定尔功。</p>
